comments: Young (ATL) crosses half-court within eight seconds.
Garland (CLE) brings his hand toward Young's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs with Young's front as he crosses over at the top of the perimeter.
Okongwu (ATL) and Markkanen (CLE) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs during rebounding.
Hunter (ATL) initiates contact across Mobley's (CLE) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Markkanen (CLE) extends slightly toward Young's (ATL) path and marginal body contact occurs with Young's side during the drive.
Huerter (ATL) brings his left hand toward Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs with Garland's side/arm at the end of the drive.
Okongwu (ATL) and Allen (CLE) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another as Allen cuts through the lane.
Okongwu (ATL) extends his right arm to defend the alley-oop attempt and incidental contact occurs with Mobley's (CLE) right forearm after the errant pass is broken up by the rim.
LeVert (CLE) initiates contact across Okongwu's (ATL) left arm as he secures the loose ball.
Garland (CLE) brings his right arm toward Gallinari's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs with Gallinari's front during the drive.
Mobley (CLE) is moving slightly forward toward Gallinari (ATL) and marginal body contact occurs as Gallinari is passing.
Markkanen (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball and intercepts the pass intended for Okongwu (ATL).
Huerter (ATL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Garland (CLE) along the sideline.
Huerter (ATL) avoids stepping out of bounds after stealing the pass.
Mobley (CLE) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Hueter (ATL) legally contests Garland's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Huerter (ATL) brushes Mobley's (CLE) right wrist and marginal contact occurs as Mobley retrieves the rebound.
Okongwu (ATL) establishes verticality and absorbs the body contact as Mobley (CLE) jumps toward Okongwu during his upward shooting motion.

Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) brings his left forearm toward Mobley's (CLE) front and marginal contact occurs as they each elevate for the rebound. Okongwu (ATL) and Mobley then make incidental arm contact with one another as they each extend an arm in pursuit of the loose ball.
Mobley (CLE) commits a take foul on Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL).
Young (ATL) and LeVert (CLE) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Huerter (ATL) engages and disengages with LeVert (CLE) during the inbound.
LeVert (CLE) commits a take foul on Young (ATL). The contact occurs prior to Young's gather and upward shooting motion.
Bogdanovic (ATL) brings his left forearm toward Mobley's (CLE) back and marginal contact occurs as Mobley mishandles the inbound pass.
Bogdanovic (ATL) legally contests Mobley's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Markkanen (CLE) attempts to commit a take foul on Young (ATL) and the contact is marginal.
